parameters:
Just ahead is my parents' bedroom. I should refrain from entering
without permission.
Yui: "Tomorrow, I'll cook dinner for you!"

\n[6]: "No, it's nothing..." (But I've had it before, and it was a
disaster...)

TV: "We interrupt for a breaking news update. According to information
just in--"

TV: "Today, the Zaidarg that appeared in the Urban District was
subdued by Pony Celes."

TV: "Today, the Zaidarg that appeared in the Urban District was
subdued by Pony Celes."

TV: "That was an emergency news bulletin. Now, onto the next news
item."

\n[6]: "So it appeared in the Urban District today. We never know when
it might show up in our district, so be careful on your way home from
school, Yui."

Yui: "Ahaha, I'm the ace of the girls' karate club. I'm not scared of
Zaidarg at all."

\n[6]: "What are you saying? This is an opponent not even the police
can handle. You absolutely must not get close!"

Yui: "What's this? Are you worried about me? That's so unlike you.
Hehehe, but thanks!"
\n[6]: "But still, who exactly is Pony Celes?"

\n[6]: "Always saving the city from Zaidarg. I think they're probably
about our age, but they're really amazing."

Yui: "Right? Who could it be~? Going to school while doing such
righteous work. They must be really hardworking~"

Yui: "Since they're working so hard, getting a few red marks here and
there should be forgivable, right~?"

\n[6]: "What's that supposed to mean? It sounds like you're talking
about yourself..."

\n[6]: "Yui, make sure you study hard so you don't get any failing
grades. I'll always help you with math if you need it."
